window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A thrilling tale of love, lies, and lethal magic.</b></p> <p>As Charlie and Ellis fight to protect their love and their people, they find themselves entangled in a web of deceit spun by an unlikely foe.</p> <p>Charlie's future with Ellis hangs in the balance when the Drow elders threaten to wipe his memories.</p> <p><b>Would they take his life?</b></p> <p>To prove his worth, the detective must solve the murder of a Drow with a mysterious past. But as he delves deeper into the investigation, he uncovers a sinister plot that could destroy everything he holds dear.</p> <p>Meanwhile, Ellis faces her own challenges when Claire sends her on a dangerous mission to retrieve vital research from a secret government lab. Trapped and running out of options, Ellis must rely on her wits and her allies to survive.</p> <p><b>With time running out and the fate of the Homestead at stake, they must confront their deepest fears and make the ultimate sacrifice. Will Charlie and Ellis unravel the mystery before it's too late? Or will they be torn apart by the very forces they're trying to save?</b></p>"; 
